<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 21:11:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴西和中国呼吁与俄罗斯和乌克兰两国进行和谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/brazil-china-call-russia-ukraine-peace-talks-with-both-countries-2024-05-23/</link><description>路透社周四看到的一份文件显示，巴西和中国周四签署了一份联合声明，呼吁两国参与就俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的冲突进行和平谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 20:11:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/brazil-china-call-russia-ukraine-peace-talks-with-both-countries-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>赫斯-雪佛龙合并投票似乎已经成熟，以微弱优势获得通过</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hess-chevron-merger-vote-appears-ripe-narrow-approval-2024-05-23/</link><description>赫斯公司 (Hess Corp) 首席执行官约翰·赫斯 (John Hess) 必须在周二之前平息股东对其处理可能成为石油行业历史上最大的合并之一的抗议：拟议以 530 亿美元将这家石油生产商出售给雪佛龙公司 (Chevron Corp)。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 18:35:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hess-chevron-merger-vote-appears-ripe-narrow-approval-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国、肯尼亚呼吁加大对发展中国家的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-kenya-call-increased-support-developing-countries-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登和肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托周四呼吁加大对肯尼亚等发展中国家的支持，包括通过中国等主要双边债权人减免债务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 18:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-kenya-call-increased-support-developing-countries-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克现在表示，他反对美国对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/elon-musk-im-against-tax-incentives-evs-2024-05-23/</link><description>特斯拉创始人埃隆·马斯克周四在巴黎对科技投资者表示，他反对美国对中国电动汽车征收关税，这与他一月份警告需要采取贸易壁垒，否则中国将“摧毁世界上大多数其他汽车公司”的态度大相径庭。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 16:15:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/elon-musk-im-against-tax-incentives-evs-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>由于交付仍然低迷，波音公司预计 2024 年将出现自由现金消耗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-now-sees-negative-free-cash-flow-2024-deliveries-remain-sluggish-2024-05-23/</link><description>该公司财务主管周四表示，波音公司在 2024 年将烧钱而不是产生现金，第二季度的交付量也不会增加，因为这家美国飞机制造商正在努力应对一场全面的危机，这场危机正在挤压其最畅销飞机的产量。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 15:45:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-now-sees-negative-free-cash-flow-2024-deliveries-remain-sluggish-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>拜登和肯尼亚鲁托承诺保护非洲民主</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-welcomes-kenyas-ruto-white-house-with-investments-promises-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周四欢迎肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托到白宫进行国事访问，承诺与非洲最强大民主国家之一的领导人在技术、安全和债务减免方面建立新时代的伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 14:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-welcomes-kenyas-ruto-white-house-with-investments-promises-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国阿里巴巴将通过发行可转换票据筹集 45 亿美元资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-alibaba-raise-45-bln-through-convertible-notes-offering-2024-05-23/</link><description>阿里巴巴集团周四表示，将出售 45 亿美元的可转换优先票据，并计划用部分收益回购美国存托股票。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 13:43:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-alibaba-raise-45-bln-through-convertible-notes-offering-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>宫一专注，水手队瞄准亚洲冠军联赛冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/miyaichi-focused-marinos-set-sights-asian-champions-league-crown-2024-05-23/</link><description>横滨水手队边锋宫市亮相信日本队能够在周六的亚洲冠军联赛决赛第二回合中保持专注，击败东道主艾因队，夺得洲际冠军。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 13:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/miyaichi-focused-marinos-set-sights-asian-champions-league-crown-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>尽管欧盟关税威胁，中国汽车制造商蔚来汽车在阿姆斯特丹开设陈列室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-carmaker-nio-unfazed-by-european-tariff-uncertainties-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车创始人李斌周四表示，尽管欧盟是否会对中国电动汽车征收关税存在不确定性，但该公司仍计划继续在欧洲扩张。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:37:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-carmaker-nio-unfazed-by-european-tariff-uncertainties-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，谷歌与富士康合作在印度生产 Pixel 手机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-ties-up-with-foxconn-make-pixel-phones-india-sources-say-2024-05-23/</link><description>两位直接知情人士周四表示，Alphabet 旗下的谷歌正计划在印度南部泰米尔纳德邦生产 Pixel 智能手机，并已与台湾富士康建立合作关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-ties-up-with-foxconn-make-pixel-phones-india-sources-say-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>大型投资者向新兴市场注入资金，掩盖了新兴市场的资金外流</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/bigger-investors-pouring-money-into-emerging-markets-belie-em-outflows-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国银行一位资深经济学家告诉路透社，大资金投资者开始在新兴市场投入更多现金，因为他们追逐回报，这可能是他们配置资金方式的结构性转变。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 11:54:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/bigger-investors-pouring-money-into-emerging-markets-belie-em-outflows-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：欧洲汽车制造商需要时间而不是关税来抵御中国竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-automakers-need-time-not-tariffs-fend-off-china-competition-2024-05-23/</link><description>行业高管在路透社的一次活动中表示，欧洲汽车巨头不会有太多时间重组其业务和产品线以与崛起的中国汽车制造商竞争，而且更严格的关税对维持现状无济于事。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-automakers-need-time-not-tariffs-fend-off-china-competition-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>起亚摆脱电动汽车需求放缓的影响推出紧凑型电动SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/kia-shrugs-off-slowing-ev-demand-launch-compact-electric-suv-2024-05-23/</link><description>起亚公司周四推出了该公司首款基于其专用电动汽车平台打造的紧凑型电动运动型多用途车，并相信即使全球电动汽车市场势头停滞，它也能通过有竞争力的价格赢得买家。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/kia-shrugs-off-slowing-ev-demand-launch-compact-electric-suv-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞标：英伟达在美联储、台湾和英国民意调查紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-23/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:03:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>由于手机销量强劲，第一季度超出预期，小米将电动汽车目标提高至 12 万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-reports-27-rise-q1-revenue-strong-smartphone-sales-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国小米表示，今年的目标是交付 12 万辆电动汽车 (EV)，高于最初的 10 万辆目标，并将实施双班制生产，以满足日益增长的电动汽车需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-reports-27-rise-q1-revenue-strong-smartphone-sales-2024-05-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>